Description: This package provides the functions necessary to perform the analysis in [Mejia et al., 2019](https://doi.org/10.1080/01621459.2019.1611582).  The package requires the INLA package, which, due to a CRAN policy, will not be installed automatically. You can obtain the two packages by running `install.packages("INLA", repos=c(getOption("repos"), INLA="https://inla.r-inla-download.org/R/stable"), dep=TRUE)`
